{"tid":392806,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳Google將全面收購HTC手機業務，並已達談判最後階段","createTime":"2017-09-08T17:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T04:01:07.000Z","uid":23677,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da04aff5006808cea57aa2a30b76ff6c4e26a61e","tid":392806,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"有台灣傳媒引述消息報道，Google將完全收購台灣電子廠商HTC（宏達電）的智能手機團隊，並已進入談判的最後階段。<br />\n<br />\n《工商時報》引述消息報道，由於Google現有硬體資源不足，未能配合硬體業務發展， 加上HTC近年出現嚴重虧損，促成了是次併購。併購涉及的 實際資金暫時未明，但消息指出價錢對Google母公司Alphabet來說不會造成任何壓力。談判亦已經進入了最後階段，最遲將會於年底前完成。<br />\n<br />\nHTC業績自2011年以來就開始出現下跌，而智能手機業務更是一蹶不振。雖然HTC順應潮流開發自家的VR裝置，但也未能一洗頹風。而對Google來說，是次買下HTC的智能手機團隊也是一個較為特別的收購。Google於2011年以125億美元買下摩托羅拉（Motorola），以加強發展硬件裝置的能力，但直至2014年賣出摩托羅拉之前都未有研發出膾炙人口的產品。鑒於這次往績，有分析指Google買下HTC團隊並不是要專門發展出新智能手機，而是製造出可配合其他線上服務如雲端儲存、AI等的相應硬件裝置。<br />\n<br />\n而在去年，Google就組成了全新硬件部門，由摩托羅拉前主席 Rick Osterloh領軍，專門發展硬件產品。這個部門目前已經研發出Pixel系列手機、Google Home擴音器、Daydream VR裝置等產品。假若Google最後成功收購HTC手機團隊，或有可能將其整合至這個硬件部門中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2017/09/08/article/35453/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2Farticle%2F35453%2F&d=cuLZz19rJ0ryePju2%2B%2Fih6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=dc2af877\" target=\"_blank\">http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2017/09/08/article/35453/</a>"},{"pid":"a81f03e584ac45a568cc9c588c22f244213e7e3e","tid":392806,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d3369f0382efedc9ff3ad10fd30765ce2a635f","tid":392806,"uid":126642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7481ca5da890293cf7666b7207470753f21a7bb1","tid":392806,"uid":517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"HTC=Help This Company"},{"pid":"c0689427a132c7576619025145811781c1d3d829","tid":392806,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T18:50:30.000Z","msg":"咁似d 台仔炒消息新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410c836984f1f80a3a29aae1ca84283a0752a17f","tid":392806,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T00:57:07.000Z","msg":"htc壽終正寢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da70124127aa34af89b09e1e8e314c05c1b9e563","tid":392806,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:23:54.000Z","msg":"轉頭收購完又賣俾大陸公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2543bd87ccb67d3a78a703f621340e7713085242","tid":392806,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉頭收購完又賣俾大陸公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}